NAME
    Acme::Licence - easily apply a licence to your code

SYNOPSIS

    use Acme::Licence; # and that's it!

INSTALLATION

    Do the usual:
	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DESCRIPTION

    All code you release to the outside world needs to have a licence.
    Acme::Licence makes it easy to apply a licence to your own code,
    and just as importantly, to let the users know what the licence is.

